description: This East Side penthouse features high-end finishes thoughtfully chosen in the 2016 construction. As you enter the living room, you're immediately welcomed by soaring 11+ foot ceilings & oversized windows framed by interior shutters. The three side exposure help to bathe the space in natural light. The chef-inspired kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line Thermador appliances, including a four-burner gas range and sleek white shaker-style cabinetry. This level also includes a private deck off the kitchen, a convenient powder room, and a laundry space. The primary suite offers two built-in closets & en-suite bath with a large tiled shower. Enjoy exclusive access to the private roof deck with incredible city views. The spacious second bedroom features two closets, including a deep storage nook, & is adjacent to a full bath with a granite vanity. The condo is finished off with one off street parking space and is centrally located to everything South Boston.
